  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help the victims of volcano eruption in DR Congo</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">After the eruption of Nyiragongo volcano in the DR of Congo, the inhabitants of the region need urgent help. The lava began to flow towards the city of Goma 20 kilometers to the south, it had flowed into the city, destroying hundreds of homes. Tens of thousands of people have been displaced. At least 31 people have died and 30,000 were forced to flee their homes. They flee with bare belongings. We have to help the children and deliver food and shelter for the victims.</narrative>
  </description>
